download_instructions.note: Some URLs point to meme template pages rather than direct image files. To download:
steps: 3. For Imgflip templates: Right-click the template image and select 'Save image as'
4. For Know Your Meme: Navigate to the photo gallery and download high-res versions
5. For GIPHY/Tenor: Click the download button and select your preferred resolution
6. For stock photo sites: May require free account for downloads

usage_tips: Use disaster/shock memes for dramatic reveals and catastrophic outcomes
Use leaving/quitting memes when describing organ failure or system shutdown
Use confusion/thinking memes for complex pathophysiology explanations
Use success memes for correct diagnosis reveals and treatment successes
Use chronic/suffering memes for ongoing health problems and patient struggles
Use comparison memes for differential diagnosis and treatment choices
